      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's really helpful for the \"scientific\" side of my paper. I'm trying to wrap my head around the sheer scale of their confidence though. Based on those ideas of \"hereditary germ plasm\" and skull shapes, how did they actually rank these different groups? If you were to summarize the hierarchy they were trying to establish, what would that look like in terms of which groups they placed at the top vs the bottom?",
